abstract: It was a grave moment, freighted with history, in the ordinarily bustling chamber.
lead_paragraph: At five minutes past noon on Thursday, something rare happened in the Senate: All senators were seated, and the chamber came to a hush as the wooden doors swung open and a team of seven House Democrats, escorted by the Senate sergeant-at-arms, marched into the chamber. It was a grave moment, freighted with history, in the ordinarily bustling chamber.
